    <title>From a nonlinear kinetic equation to a volume-exclusion chemotaxis model via asymptotic preserving methods</title>
	   		    
    
		<meta name="keywords" content="Kinetic equations, asymptotic preserving (AP) methods, chemotaxis equations, diffusion approximation, velocity-jump processes" />
